<subSubSection pageId="196" pageNumber="475" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="196.[180,1388,297,844]" pageId="196" pageNumber="475">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[182,293,376,409]" pageId="196" pageNumber="475">Habitat.</emphasis>
Wet elfin forests, heavily wooded canyons, living grasses and rushes near swamps, and crop fields at elevations of 1900-2860 m.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
